h2. NAME

dojo4_template_tidy

h2. INSTALL

# copy dojo4_template_tidy into ExpressionEngine "third_party" folder
# copy dojo4_themes into ExpressionEngine "themes/third_party" folder

h2. SYNOPSIS
  
Attempts to add classic "tidy" functionality to the ExpressionEngine control panel, specifically to the template modification screen.

h2. HISTORY
  
h3. 0.0.1

Initial release. Pre-alpha, use at your own risk, likely to break things, totally experimental.

